data.description: ** The Seller is willing to help with closing costs** Welcome to your dream home in the beautiful Beechtree community! This exquisite single-family home boasts luxury and space, offering the perfect blend of comfort and elegance. Nestled on a generous corner lot, this residence provides ample privacy and a sense of openness. As you approach, you'll be captivated by its charming curb appeal and lush landscaping. The well-maintained exterior sets the tone for what lies within. Step inside, and you'll find a spacious and thoughtfully designed layout. With five bedrooms, three full bathrooms, and one half bathroom, this home accommodates families of all sizes with ease. The bright and inviting living spaces are adorned with high-end finishes and stylish touches throughout. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a chef's delight. Equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, it's perfect for preparing gourmet meals or quick family dinners. The adjacent formal dining room is grand enough to comfortably accommodate a table for 10, making it ideal for hosting memorable gatherings with friends and loved ones. Upstairs, the primary bedroom is a true sanctuary. It features a generous floor plan, complete with a cozy sitting room where you can unwind and relax. The walk-in closet offers ample space for your wardrobe, ensuring you have room for all your fashion treasures. On the top floor, you'll discover three additional bedrooms, each generously sized and suitable for queen-size beds. These rooms provide flexibility for family members or guests, ensuring everyone has their own comfortable space. The basement is a versatile area with a large bedroom and a full bathroom, making it perfect for guests or as a private retreat. Beyond that, there's an unfinished area, a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch. Whether you envision a home theater, a fitness room, or additional storage, the possibilities are endless. One of the standout features of this home is the spacious backyard. It provides an outdoor oasis for entertaining, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. Whether you're grilling with friends or lounging with a good book, this backyard is sure to become one of your favorite spots. Located in the sought-after Beechtree community, this home offers not only the comforts of luxury living but also the benefits of a vibrant neighborhood. With scenic walking trails, parks, and community amenities, you'll have everything you need right at your doorstep. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning Beechtree residence your forever home. With its exceptional features and prime location, it's a rare find that promises a lifetime of memories.
